          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> carrot[s]</strong> into rounds (no need to peel!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1725365143203-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1725365143203-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
