    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir in your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and add 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span>[550ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>soft cheese</strong>,<strong> Dijon mustard</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong></p>",
