      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong>, season with a grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>hotpot filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
