      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into discs</p><p>Carefully arrange the<strong> potato discs</strong> over the top of the <strong>hotpot filling</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the dish in the oven for an initial 25 min</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
