    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 25 min, trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until the beans are tender and lightly golden, the hotpot is bubbling and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
